| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0921 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e2e59262-22ce-512a-8f42-ae5fc8bff8f4"
